        OCaml-R installation


*** What you need ***
- OCaml 3.12.0 or above installed
- R >= 2.9 with development libraries

*** How to compile ***

  make build
  opam install .


*** How to use ***


[gesundheit:~ 16:29]$ocaml
        Objective Caml version 3.12.1

